headline.print_headline: Role Players Key UConn's 63-53 Win Over Florida
headline.main: Role Players Key UConn's 63-53 Win Over Florida

lead_paragraph: Connecticut's 2011 national championship has been characterized as a one-man effort by Kemba Walker. Good as he was, he still needed help from teammates Jeremy Lamb, Alex Oriakhi and Shabazz Napier.
